 The 13th edition of the headies award is scheduled to hold today, 19th of October 2019. Burna Boy clinched the spot for the most-nominated artist. In one of the categories, Burna Boy’s Album ‘Outside’ will be competing with three other popular artistes for the “Album of the Year” award. All of the albums in this category are with no-doubt fantastic and evergreen ―  Adekunle Gold (Ire), Falz (Moral Instruction), and Kizz Daniel (No Bad Songz). Continue reading Headies Award 2019: Adekunle Gold, Burna Boy, Falz, Kizz Daniel battles for ‘Album of the Year’ award at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard